data.description:
Shalimar, FL - Apartment Building 

Very well maintained duplex with spacious living room, two bedrooms, full bath and utility room. Living room has ceramic tile with carpet in the bedrooms. Sliding glass door leads to back patio. One car garage. Smoking and pets are not authorized.
